properties.areaDesc: Coastal waters from St. Augustine to Flagler Beach FL out 20 NM
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 10 at 1:42AM EST until January 11 at 11:00PM EST by NWS Jacksonville FL
properties.description:
* WHAT...Seas 5 to 7 feet expected.

* WHERE...Coastal waters from St. Augustine to Flagler Beach FL
out 20 NM.

* WHEN...From 10 PM this evening to 11 PM EST Saturday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 10 PM THIS EVENING TO 11 PM EST SATURDAY
